Sally O'Neil https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sally_O%27Neil 0 Sally O'Neil (born Virginia Louise Concepta Noonan, October 23, 1908 – June 18, 1968) was an American film actress of the 1920s. She appeared in more than 40 films, often with her name above the title.
